  "remarks": "\nAsia Sun Group Company Limited, is owned or controlled directly by Zaw Min Tun, a member of Asia Sun Trading Company Limited, a person involved in the repression of the civilian population of Myanmar by making available economic resources (aviation fuel) directly or indirectly to or for the benefit of the Myanmar security forces.\n",
